"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"A qualified security layer may also bring an invisible benefit: a massive data availability layer. For example, Ethereum will initially have 64 shard chains, and then expand to 1024 shard chains. According to Moore's Law and Nielsen's Law, its data availability may be expanded to several GB/s. . Such an amazing increase in data availability will never be realized on a centralized integrated blockchain, which effectively solves the trilemma of the blockchain. I predict that rollup may expand the TPS of Ethereum to 15 million in 10 years. At that time, if there are other data availability solutions, Ethereum's TPS may even reach a higher level.\",\"timestamp\":1634226168,\"title\":\"Mass data availability layer! !\"},\"digest\":\"mgywuT5G4pzYB54do0NbmYTRhuGgF1td8un6tZrEEPc\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x4aE66AA2598A131cDE3Fbc815443b9A829e46c22\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"RKc9FXpqEJviIU_PIjF7LjNiVVM-th7fDRiQwTk8J_s\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"9wPk6jbK36M3KhGJhwo4oBM-u9RBYd0MzziSxakVu8o\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"eWiZ8w9fczKwP0TuZcYISTF__uMM28SnSqXuYFZnAkXAkSbYwAYZoUnwz1-8C0GCeXOtUQ8JM9XmJDw5KPkNmg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xdc265ec8639071f38b4c4a0ec52936cb0712da81395e53c92fda49f612a623b355edd01b8365d3b2cf143e363d38f88eb45d8a25033d33c415871fe39b49eecf1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"RKc9FXpqEJviIU_PIjF7LjNiVVM-th7fDRiQwTk8J_s\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"9wPk6jbK36M3KhGJhwo4oBM-u9RBYd0MzziSxakVu8o\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"mgywuT5G4pzYB54do0NbmYTRhuGgF1td8un6tZrEEPc\"}"